extendedInfo.description: City Jump is executing mysterious task, jumping between buildings, to avoid obstacles on the wall, to kill monsters, birds, and other enemies on the way.* Tap screen to jump* Kill enemy by jumping in the air* Avoid hurdles on walls* POW UP when killing 3 enemies of the same kind.
